<%- include('header') -%>

<section id="shipping-policy" style="margin-top: 16vw">
  <div style="padding: 2vw; margin-left: 1vw">
    <h3>Shipping Policy</h3>
    <br />

    <h4>1. What is the estimated delivery time?</h4>
    <p>
      Delivery timelines depend on various factors such as product availability,
      delivery location, warehouse processing time, and courier partner
      serviceability. The estimated delivery time within India is
      <strong>3–7 working days</strong>. Deliveries to remote or non-metro
      regions may take longer.
    </p>
    <p>
      While we make every effort to deliver orders on or before the estimated
      date, delays may occur due to courier issues, weather conditions, or
      operational disruptions. If your order is delayed beyond a reasonable
      period, you may request a cancellation and receive a full refund.
    </p>
    <br />

    <h4>2. How much is the delivery cost / shipping fee?</h4>
    <p>
      Shipping charges vary depending on the product, delivery location, and
      courier partner. Most products on <strong>Sahii.in</strong> include free
      shipping unless otherwise mentioned. Please review your order summary
      before checkout to view the exact shipping charges, if applicable.
    </p>
    <br />

    <h4>3. What are the rules for Cash on Delivery (COD) orders?</h4>
    <p>
      For COD orders, an advance payment of <strong>₹150</strong> is required at
      the time of placing the order. The remaining amount must be paid in cash
      upon delivery. This advance helps cover partial shipping and verification
      costs and ensures order authenticity.
    </p>
    <br />

    <h4>4. When will deliveries take place?</h4>
    <p>
      Our courier partners deliver orders between
      <strong>9:00 AM and 6:00 PM</strong> on working days. If you are unable to
      receive the parcel, please ensure that someone (family, friend, neighbor,
      security guard) is available at the address to accept the shipment on your
      behalf.
    </p>
    <br />

    <h4>5. What if I am not available to receive the shipment?</h4>
    <p>
      Couriers generally attempt delivery 2–3 times. If all attempts fail, the
      parcel is marked as <strong>RTO (Return to Origin)</strong> and sent back
      to us. A reshipping charge will apply if you want the order dispatched
      again to the same or a new address.
    </p>
    <br />

    <h4>6. How will I be notified about my order?</h4>
    <p>You will receive timely updates at every stage:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Order confirmation via Email or WhatsApp</li>
      <li>Tracking number once the order is dispatched</li>
      <li>Live tracking via the “Track Order” page on our website</li>
      <li>Notification when the parcel is out for delivery</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      We aim to keep you fully informed until your order reaches you safely.
    </p>
    <br />

    <h4>7. How will the packaging look upon delivery?</h4>
    <p>
      All items from <strong>Sahii Spare Parts</strong> are packed in strong,
      tamper-proof packaging designed to protect delicate components and ensure
      safe delivery.
    </p>
    <br />

    <h4>
      8. What should I do if my package shows as delivered but I haven't
      received it?
    </h4>
    <p>
      If your tracking status shows “Delivered” but you haven’t received the
      package:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Check with family members, neighbors, or building security.</li>
      <li>Wait a few hours (sometimes courier status updates prematurely).</li>
      <li>
        Look around the premises (doorstep, gate, reception desk, guard cabin,
        etc.).
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      If still not found, contact our support team within
      <strong>24 hours</strong> of the delivery status update. Claims raised
      after 24 hours may not be accepted due to courier partner policies.
    </p>
    <br />

    <h4>9. Need Help?</h4>
    <p>For any questions regarding shipping or tracking, contact us:</p>
    <p>
      <strong>WhatsApp / Call:</strong> +91 92171 37095<br />
      <strong>Email:</strong> support@sahii.in<br />
      <strong>Support Hours:</strong> Monday to Saturday, 10:00 AM to 7:00 PM
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include('footer') -%>
